AlphaForge AI
Agentic AI-Powered Financial Intelligence Platform

Transforming raw financial data into intelligent investment insights through autonomous AI agents.

🌟 Overview

AlphaForge AI is an Agentic AI financial research platform that automates company analysis by combining Large Language Models (LLMs), Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG), real-time financial APIs, and a multi-agent architecture.

Instead of relying on a single AI model to answer every question, AlphaForge delegates specialized tasks to autonomous agents—each responsible for gathering, analyzing, and synthesizing a different aspect of a company's financial health.

The result is a comprehensive, explainable, and data-driven investment report generated within seconds.

