⚙️ Installation

Clone the repository

git clone <repository-url>
cd AlphaForge

Create a virtual environment

python -m venv venv

Activate it

Windows
venv\Scripts\activate
macOS/Linux
source venv/bin/activate

Install dependencies

pip install -r requirements.txt

Configure your environment variables

GROQ_API_KEY=YOUR_KEY
NEWS_API_KEY=YOUR_KEY

Run the server

uvicorn main:app --reload

Open:

http://localhost:8000/docs
🔌 API Highlights
Endpoint	Description
/financial/{ticker}	Financial analysis
/news/{ticker}	Latest company news
/compare/{ticker}	Competitor benchmarking
/charts/{ticker}	Financial chart data
/report/{ticker}	AI-generated research report
🧩 How AlphaForge Works
User submits a company ticker.
The Report Agent orchestrates the workflow.
Specialized AI agents execute tasks independently.
External APIs provide financial and news data.
RAG retrieves relevant contextual information from ChromaDB.
Groq LLM synthesizes insights.
AlphaForge returns a comprehensive financial intelligence report.
🎯 Why Agentic AI?

Traditional AI systems rely on one prompt to solve everything.

AlphaForge breaks the problem into specialized tasks executed by independent AI agents, making the platform:

More scalable
Easier to extend
Better at reasoning
More maintainable
Modular by design
Faster to evolve
